DocAttribute.Name: PredefinedType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Predefined generic types for an external spatial element that are specified in an enumeration. There might be property sets defined specifically for each predefined type.

DocAttribute.Name: BoundedBy
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to a set of _IfcRelSpaceBoundary_'s that defines the physical or virtual delimitation of that external spacial element against physical or virtual boundaries.
